/www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/manic_street_decline_fall_alex_lake_2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/manic_street_decline_fall_alex_lake_2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/manic_street_decline_fall_alex_lake_2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/manic_street_decline_fall_alex_lake_2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/manic-street-preachers">Manic Street Preachers</a>带着他们成功的新单曲“Decline &amp; Fall”回归。看看下面。 </p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="468" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/manic-street-preachers-ultra-vivid-lament-nicky-wire-james-dean-bradfield-3020202"><b>躁狂街传教士接受采访：“我们通过遗忘来谈论自己”</b></a></li></ul><p>这首歌<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/manic-street-preachers-tease-new-material-so-much-for-the-decline-fall-3787472">整周都在被调侃</a>，这首歌是在乐队 1994 年开创性专辑《The Holy Bible》30 周年纪念日前夕发布的，也是他们自 2021 年广受好评的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/manic-street-preachers-score-first-uk-number-one-album-in-23-years-with-the-ultra-vivid-lament-3048680">排行榜冠军</a>第 14 张专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/manic-street-preachers-the-ultra-vivid-lament-review-3035938">《The Ultra Vivid Lament》</a>以来的第一首新作品。</p><p>这首单曲采用了他们之前唱片中一些复古未来主义的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/abba">ABBA</a>风格的声音，并与《Resistance Is Futile》和《Everything Must Go》的竞技场欢快声相遇，但受到了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-skids">The Skids</a>和《Gran Turismo》中 Manics 的影响而向前发展。 &#39;时代的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/THE-CARDIGANS">羊毛衫</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-war-on-drugs">毒品战争</a>。</p><p> “在音乐上，我们试图通过‘Decline &amp; Fall’创造前进的动力——一首利用过去将其推向未来的歌曲——歌词是一种认识和理解——庆祝仍然存在的微小奇迹，同时接受和拥抱管理“衰落”，“Decline &amp; Fall”乐队说道。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Manic Street Preachers - 衰落与堕落（官方音频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/viRpkxdBDWA?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>这首歌是在乐队位于纽波特的 Door To The River 工作室和蒙茅斯传奇的 Rockfield Studios 录制的，由定期合作者 Dave Eringa 和 Loz Williams 制作，并由 Caesar Edmunds（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/BEACH-HOUSE">Beach House</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/SUEDE">Suede</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/wet-leg">Wet Leg</a> ）混音。</p><p>乐队在 6 月接受<a href="https://www.loudersound.com/features/nicky-wire-tour-interview" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i>Louder Sound</i></a>采访时讨论了他们即将推出的第 15 张专辑，当时他们称这张专辑“已完成 90%”，并可能于 2025 年 1 月或 2 月发行。</p><p> “它有很大的能量，尽管我感觉不是特别有活力，”贝斯手兼作词家<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/NICKY-WIRE">Nicky Wire</a>说。 “其中一首歌曲像是我们最喜欢的两个乐队 The Cardigans 和 The Skids 的混合体，另一首听起来像是<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/DINOSAUR-JR">Dinosaur Jr</a>演奏的《Come Up And See Me》（由 Steve Harley 和 Cockney Rebel 演唱）。” </p><figure id="attachment_3788827" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3788827" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3788827" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/manic_street_decline_fall_alex_lake_1.jpg" alt="躁狂街传教士，2024 年。图片来源：Alex Lake" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/manic_street_decline_fall_alex_lake_1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/manic_street_decline_fall_alex_lake_1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/manic_street_decline_fall_alex_lake_1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/manic_street_decline_fall_alex_lake_1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/manic_street_decline_fall_alex_lake_1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/manic_street_decline_fall_alex_lake_1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3788827" class="wp-caption-text">躁狂街传教士，2024 年。图片来源：Alex Lake</figcaption></figure><p>这位威尔士偶像和前 NME Godlike Genius 获奖者<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/manic-street-preachers-share-unreleased-song-rosebud-from-new-know-your-enemy-reissue-3274690">于 2022 年发行了专辑《Know Your Enemy》</a> ，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/manic-street-preachers-announce-20th-anniversary-re-issue-of-lifeblood-3583696">于今年早些时候发行了《Lifeblood》</a> ，而去年 Nicky Wire <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/manics-nicky-wire-surprise-releases-new-solo-album-intimism-3464073">出人意料地发行了他的第二张个人专辑《Intimism》</a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/manic-street-preachers-nicky-wire-announces-new-art-exhibition-in-wales-3778384">Wire 目前正在彭布罗克郡的纳贝斯博物馆举办一场<i>名为“我的小帝国”</i>的艺术展，展览将持续到 12 月</a>，其中展出了 26 件作品，展示了他对宝丽来照片的喜爱。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="躁狂街传教士访谈：关于“抵抗是徒劳的”、生存以及他们的未来" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/y-S8ACSuMeM?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>乐队还计划于明天（8 月 30 日）一次性放映音乐会电影<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/manic-street-preachers-unveil-first-clip-of-new-film-be-pure-be-vigilant-behave-1555173"><i>《BePure-BeVigilant-Behave</i></a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/manic-street-preachers-to-celebrate-30th-anniversary-of-the-holy-bible-with-special-film-screening-3765943">》，以庆祝其 1994 年专辑《The Holy Bible》发行 30 周年</a>。</p><p> Manics 最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/heres-what-manic-street-preachers-and-suede-played-as-they-kicked-off-their-co-headline-uk-tour-3770172">与 Suede 完成了英国联合巡演</a>，并已确定将在一月份在日本举行的 Rockin&#39; On Sonic 音乐节上与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pulp">Pulp</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/weezer">Weezer</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/primal-scream">Primal Scream</a>一起<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pulps-first-gig-of-2025-confirmed-with-manic-street-preachers-weezer-primal-scream-3784018">演出</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-manic-street-preachers-triumphant-new-single-decline-fall-3788823">聆听 Manic Street Preachers 的胜利新单曲《Decline &amp; Fall》</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
