m/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Marilyn-Manson-and-Evan-Rachel-Wood-Posing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Marilyn-Manson-and-Evan-Rachel-Wood-Posing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Marilyn-Manson-and-Evan-Rachel-Wood-Posing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Marilyn-Manson-and-Evan-Rachel-Wood-Posing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Marilyn-Manson-and-Evan-Rachel-Wood-Posing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Marilyn-Manson-and-Evan-Rachel-Wood-Posing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/Marilyn-Manson">玛丽莲·曼森 (Marilyn Manson)</a>指控埃文·雷切尔·伍德 (Evan Rachel Wood) 伪造了一封致联邦调查局 (FBI) 的信件，试图抹黑他的形象。</p><p> 2022 年 3 月，曼森<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/marilyn-manson-sues-evan-rachel-wood-for-defamation-3173472">对这位女演员及其前伴侣提起诽谤诉讼</a>，声称这位音乐家在她十几岁的时候就开始为她打扮，并“多年来对我进行了可怕的虐待”。</p><p>作为回应，曼森<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/marilyn-manson-denies-abuse-allegations-calls-recent-claims-horrible-distortions-of-reality-2870187">否认了所有指控</a>，并在诉讼中声称伍德“招募、协调并迫使”女性对这位音乐家做出虚假陈述。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/marilyn-manson-defamation-case-against-evan-rachel-wood-mostly-dismissed-by-us-judge-3441811">该案的关键主张已于去年5月被驳回</a>。</p><p>现在，曼森在与伍德的新诉讼中声称，她伪造了联邦调查局一名真正特工的信件，以此来抹黑他的形象。他声称这封信让他看起来像是在接受某种联邦调查，而他所谓的受害者也处于危险之中。</p><p>据<a href="https://www.tmz.com/2024/08/28/marilyn-manson-appeals-evan-rachel-wood-case-dismissal/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>TMZ 报道</em></a>，曼森辩称，他的前未婚妻捏造了针对他的性虐待指控，并将联邦调查局的信件包含在该媒体获得的文件中，并分享伍德签署了一份声明，声明她没有伪造这封信。不过，她并没有否认这是伪造的。 </p><figure id="attachment_3579552" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3579552" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3579552" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Marilyn-Manson-Evan-Rachel-Wood@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Marilyn-Manson-Evan-Rachel-Wood@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Marilyn-Manson-Evan-Rachel-Wood@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Marilyn-Manson-Evan-Rachel-Wood@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Marilyn-Manson-Evan-Rachel-Wood@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Marilyn-Manson-Evan-Rachel-Wood@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Marilyn-Manson-Evan-Rachel-Wood@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3579552" class="wp-caption-text">玛丽莲·曼森和埃文·蕾切尔·伍德，2006 年。（约翰·希勒/WireImage/Getty Images 拍摄）</figcaption></figure><p>这位摇滚明星<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/marilyn-manson-defamation-case-against-evan-rachel-wood-mostly-dismissed-by-us-judge-3441811">最初对伍德提出的指控被法官驳回</a>，但现在他声称事实并未得到全部考虑，并试图重提此案。</p><p>今年早些时候，有消息称<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/marilyn-manson-ordered-to-pay-even-more-legal-fees-totalling-500000-3588965">曼森被勒令支付更多与此案相关的法律费用</a>，使总额达到近 500,000 美元（396,000 英镑）。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/marilyn-manson-ordered-to-pay-evan-rachel-woods-legal-fees-after-defamation-suit-dismissed-3579264">这位音乐家被责令向伍德支付约 326,000 美元的律师费</a>。据报道，曼森将支付艺术家伊尔玛·戈尔的律师费，后者被列为第二被告，并在诽谤诉讼中被描述为伍德“分分合合的浪漫伴侣”。</p><p>据报道，戈尔欠债超过 16 万美元，曼森的欠债总额接近 50 万美元。这些补偿是根据加州的反 SLAPP 法规授予的，该法规规定，因言论自由而受到不公平起诉的被告可以让原告支付其律师费。 </p><figure id="attachment_3512690" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3512690" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3512690" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Marilyn-Manson-and-Evan-Rachel-Wood-posing-1.jpg" alt="玛丽莲·曼森和埃文·雷切尔·伍德。摄影：Eric Charbonneau/WireImage for Disney Pictures via GETTY" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Marilyn-Manson-and-Evan-Rachel-Wood-posing-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Marilyn-Manson-and-Evan-Rachel-Wood-posing-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Marilyn-Manson-and-Evan-Rachel-Wood-posing-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Marilyn-Manson-and-Evan-Rachel-Wood-posing-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Marilyn-Manson-and-Evan-Rachel-Wood-posing-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Marilyn-Manson-and-Evan-Rachel-Wood-posing-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3512690" class="wp-caption-text">玛丽莲·曼森和埃文·蕾切尔·伍德。摄影：Eric Charbonneau/WireImage for Disney Pictures via GETTY</figcaption></figure><p>在 2021 年的一篇 Instagram 帖子中，伍德最初<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/evan-rachel-wood-and-other-women-make-allegations-of-abuse-against-marilyn-manson-2869492">指责曼森在她十几岁的时候对她进行培养，并多年来“可怕”地虐待她</a>。 “我被洗脑并被操纵屈服，”她写道。 “我已经厌倦了生活在报复、诽谤或勒索的恐惧之中。我来这里是为了揭露这个危险的人，并在他毁掉更多人的生命之前，揭露那些为他提供便利的行业。我与众多受害者站在一起，他们将不再保持沉默。”</p><p>在她首次发帖后，至少有四名女性分享了她们自己关于曼森的故事，以声援伍德。曼森否认了所有五名指控者的指控，称其为“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/marilyn-manson-denies-abuse-allegations-calls-recent-claims-horrible-distortions-of-reality-2870187">对现实的可怕扭曲</a>”。</p><p>此后，曼森遭遇一系列性侵案件。指控者包括<em>《权力的游戏》</em>女演员兼前女友埃斯梅·比安科和前女友阿什莉·摩根·史密斯莱恩。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/marilyn-manson-sexual-assault-case-dismissed-3374849">Smithline 提起的诉讼已被驳回</a>，而曼森<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/marilyn-manson-says-assault-allegations-are-co-ordinated-attack-against-him-3005962">以“毫无根据”为由否认了比安科的指控</a>，并于 2023 年 1 月<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/games-of-thrones-actor-esme-bianco-and-marilyn-manson-reach-settlement-in-sexual-assault-lawsuit-3386310">与她达成和解</a>。</p><p> 2023 年 9 月，他还被一位名叫 Jane Doe 的人指控——不过，她的案件<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/marilyn-manson-reportedly-settles-sexual-assault-lawsuit-a-week-ahead-of-trial-3506325">在开庭前一周就得到了和解</a>。</p><p><strong>如需有关英国性骚扰、攻击和强奸的帮助、建议或更多信息，请访问<a href="https://rapecrisis.org.uk/find-a-centre/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">强奸危机慈善网站</a>。在美国，请访问<a href="https://www.rainn.org/index.php" target="_blank" rel="noopener">RAINN</a> 。</strong></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/marilyn-manson-accuses-evan-rachel-wood-of-forging-a-letter-to-the-fbi-3788772">玛丽莲·曼森 (Marilyn Manson) 指控埃文·蕾切尔·伍德 (Evan Rachel Wood) 伪造一封致联邦调查局 (FBI) 的信件的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
